dition of Automation 2014 will be held from October 15 to 18, 2014 at the Bombay Exhibition Centre, in Mumbai - the financial capital of India.  \r\n END ... Automation 2014 joins hands with the Government of Republic of Rwanda for promoting Indian industries in the African continent ... Niranjan Mudholkar ... 	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
